00:10:06,373 --> 00:10:08,842 line:-1
in GrÃ¼sse aus Cupertino.


227
00:10:10.210 --> 00:10:11.578 line:-1 align:center
But I don't have support


228
00:10:11,612 --> 00:10:14,281 line:-1
in the Fast path for Chinese.


